Characteristics: 1st generation EGFR inhibitor drug resistant cells

GROWTH_PATTERN: Adherent, single cells and loosely attached clusters
Mixed: floating aggregates of round cells with some attached cells
Adherent, large-sized epithelial cells that float at high cell densities
Suspension, floating aggregates of large cell clusters
round up and remain loosely attached

Media_Condition: DMEM 10% + 0.1mM NEAA, 1mM sodium pyruvate, 0.05mg/ml Gentamicin, 10mM HEPES, 1% P/S (for MC-38)
